                            <comment id="15423675" author="jmspaggi" created="Wed, 17 Aug 2016 00:39:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I like this thread!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Another thing related to the bulk load. If someone bulkloads a cell wich is WAY too big, the region server might not be able to load it. Like, a 2GB cell. And will fail. Might be nice to detect that and alert the user/log the issue/skip the cell...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
